                            <comment id="12566027" author="bryanduxbury" created="Wed, 6 Feb 2008 06:03:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch removes the close method from the connection, deprecates the close method in HTable (and turns it into a noop), and gets rid of the checkClosed method (only used internally) in HTable. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This patch also modifies the unit tests to stop using the close method on HTable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12566029" author="jimk" created="Wed, 6 Feb 2008 06:15:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12567174" author="stack" created="Fri, 8 Feb 2008 19:45:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 on patch but doesn&apos;t apply to TRUNK.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;FYI, empty finally&apos;s would be better removed altogether.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12567175" author="bryanduxbury" created="Fri, 8 Feb 2008 19:47:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Old patch didn&apos;t apply cleanly anymore.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
